Superior Warmth for Every Activity

Cold weather never stopped you before. Enjoy the outdoors in comfortable, cozy fleece jackets from The North Face®. Explore lightweight, midweight and heavyweight women’s fleece jackets now.

A super soft, fleece-lined jacket is perfect for cold-weather adventures. Shop women’s fleece zip-up hoodies, vests, jackets and Sherpa pullovers to find the perfect insulation for your favorite activities. Look for fleece-lined jackets with FuseForm™ for targeted warmth and breathability in key areas, or shop full fleece jackets for women for complete warmth everywhere you go. For cold-weather summits, choose a fleece jacket with Ventrix™ dynamic-venting insulation to promote breathability and moisture management while you move. Stay cozy and comfortable, no matter the weather.
